OL,3,CWhy Criccieth holds a special place in
OL,4,CD-Day history
OL,6,FFor over a year, French commandos
OL,7,Flived in a small town in north Wales
OL,8,Fand trained on the beaches and in the
OL,9,Fmountains of Snowdonia.
OL,11,FIt was 80 years ago that the town of
OL,12,FCriccieth found out they were
OL,13,Fexpecting around 100 new guests. They
OL,14,Fwere the Kieffer commandos, a group of
OL,15,Fexiles who took their name from their
OL,16,Fleader, Philippe Kieffer.
