OL,3,CWhy Criccieth holds a special place in
OL,4,CD-Day history
OL,6,FSarah Davidson, part of the project,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I'm learning a great deal. I
OL,8,Fprobably did it in school, but didn't
OL,9,Ftake much notice. But when it's
OL,10,Fbrought to life with the experience
OL,11,Fwe've had in the last few weeks, it's
OL,12,Fdifferent altogether."
